Wednesday, October 26, 1988

MERIT DOCKET

88-1263. McDonald Equipment Co. v. Jess Howard Electric Co.

Lake County, No. 12-144. On motion to dismiss. Motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.

On motion for leave to file memorandum in support instanter. Motion denied.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Locher, Holmes, Douglas, Wright and H. Brown, JJ., concur.
